                    What was John's average speed for the entire trip, including the time spent at the store
                </p>
            </statement>
        </exercise>
        <exercise>
            <statement>
                <p>
                    A hiker covered <m>\textbf{ 12 km in 3 hours}</m>. After taking a <m>\textbf{15 minute}</m> break, 
